## Implementation Commands

### Full Audit
```bash
# Scan all skills
ls -la .claude/skills/

# Check each skill
for skill in .claude/skills/*/SKILL.md; do
  echo "Checking: $skill"
  # Validate YAML
  head -10 "$skill" | grep -E "^(name|description|allowed-tools):"
  # Check for kaizen section
  grep -c "Kaizen:" "$skill"
done
```

### Validate Shared References
```bash
# Find all references to shared docs
grep -r "shared/" .claude/skills/*/SKILL.md

# Verify files exist
for ref in factory-rules forbidden-patterns testing-patterns critical-rules clickhouse-queries; do
  if [ -f ".claude/shared/$ref.md" ]; then
    echo "✅ $ref.md exists"
  else
    echo "❌ $ref.md missing"
  fi
done
```

### Check for Outdated Patterns
```bash
# Forbidden patterns
grep -r "Time\.now" .claude/skills/*/SKILL.md
grep -r "allow_any_instance_of" .claude/skills/*/SKILL.md
grep -r "\.to_s(:db)" .claude/skills/*/SKILL.md

# Docker violations
grep -r "bundle exec" .claude/skills/*/SKILL.md | grep -v "docker\|make\|bin/d"
```

## Integration with /orchestrate

Update `/orchestrate` to include periodic kaizen checks:

```markdown
### After successful workflows:
┌─ KAIZEN CHECK ────────────────────────────────┐
│ IF workflow completed successfully THEN       │
